title: This home stands out! Res Lease in Austin. 4 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: You must see this gorgeous 1-story 4 bedrooms, 2 bathroom home in Austin, TX just waiting for you.

While the rest of additional bedrooms share a full bathroom with double vanity and a bathub perfect for relaxing after a long day.
Don't miss out on seeing the fenced private backyard, with its big green lawn, i'ts perfect to enjoy with family or friends.
